import React from 'react';
import {
    Box,
    Button,
    Container,
    Grid,
    Typography,
    Card,
    CardContent,
    CardMedia,
    AppBar,
    Toolbar,
    IconButton
} from '@mui/material';
import {
    SportsTennis,
    Event,
    Group,
    School,
    Menu as MenuIcon
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const LandingPage = () => {
    const features = [
        {
            icon: <SportsTennis sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />,
            title: 'Quadras Profissionais',
            description: 'Quadras de alta qualidade com diferentes superfícies para sua melhor experiência.'
        },
        {
            icon: <Event sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />,
            title: 'Torneios',
            description: 'Participe de torneios regulares e melhore suas habilidades competitivas.'
        },
        {
            icon: <School sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />,
            title: 'Aulas',
            description: 'Professores qualificados para todos os níveis de jogo.'
        },
        {
            icon: <Group sx={{ fontSize: 40 }} />,
            title: 'Comunidade',
            description: 'Faça parte de uma comunidade apaixonada por tênis.'
        }
    ];

    return (
        <Box>
            {/* Navbar */}
            <AppBar position="static" color="transparent" elevation={0}>
                <Toolbar>
                    <IconButton edge="start" color="inherit" aria-label="menu">
                        <MenuIcon />
                    </IconButton>
                    <Typography variant="h6" component="div" sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                        Tennis Club
                    </Typography>
                    <Button color="inherit">Login</Button>
                    <Button color="primary" variant="contained" sx={{ ml: 2 }}>
                        Cadastrar
                    </Button>
                </Toolbar>
            </AppBar>

            {/* Hero Section */}
            <Box
                sx={{
                    bgcolor: 'background.paper',
                    pt: 8,
                    pb: 6,
                    backgroundImage: 'linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url(https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?tennis-court)',
                    backgroundSize: 'cover',
                    backgroundPosition: 'center',
                    color: 'white',
                    minHeight: '500px',
                    display: 'flex',
                    alignItems: 'center'
                }}
            >
                <Container maxWidth="md">
                    <Typography
                        component="h1"
                        variant="h2"
                        align="center"
                        gutterBottom
                    >
                        Bem-vindo ao Tennis Club
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="h5" align="center" paragraph>
                        O melhor clube de tênis da região com estrutura completa para sua prática esportiva
                    </Typography>
                    <Box sx={{ mt: 4, display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
                        <Button variant="contained" size="large">
                            Agendar Quadra
                        </Button>
                        <Button variant="outlined" size="large" sx={{ color: 'white', borderColor: 'white' }}>
                            Conhecer Mais
                        </Button>
                    </Box>
                </Container>
            </Box>

            {/* Features Section */}
            <Container sx={{ py: 8 }} maxWidth="lg">
                <Grid container spacing={4}>
                    {features.map((feature, index) => (
                        <Grid item key={index} xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
                            <Card
                                sx={{
                                    height: '100%',
                                    display: 'flex',
                                    flexDirection: 'column',
                                    alignItems: 'center',
                                    textAlign: 'center',
                                    p: 2
                                }}
                            >
                                <Box sx={{ p: 2, color: 'primary.main' }}>
                                    {feature.icon}
                                </Box>
                                <CardContent>
                                    <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2">
                                        {feature.title}
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Typography>
                                        {feature.description}
                                    </Typography>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        </Grid>
                    ))}
                </Grid>
            </Container>

            {/* Footer */}
            <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', p: 6 }} component="footer">
                <Typography variant="h6" align="center" gutterBottom>
                    Tennis Club
                </Typography>
                <Typography
                    variant="subtitle1"
                    align="center"
                    color="text.secondary"
                    component="p"
                >
                    Entre em contato: (XX) XXXX-XXXX
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" align="center">
                    {'Copyright © '}
                    Tennis Club {new Date().getFullYear()}
                    {'.'}
                </Typography>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    );
};

export default LandingPage;
